# metsanpeitto theme for Ghostty
# Official palette mapping from fallwith/metsanpeitto.nvim
# Usage:
#  1. Place this file at ~/.config/ghostty/themes/metsanpeitto
#  2. In your Ghostty config file (likely ~/.config/ghostty/config), set the
#     theme via `theme = metsanpeitto`

